# Environment Variables Example
# There are currently no required environment variables for the Muskan Mehndi Art frontend.
# If you add third-party integrations (Supabase, Stripe, etc.) in the future, list their placeholder variables here.

# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=your-supabase-url
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-supabase-anon-key
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key-never-expose-to-client
